show.description: Elvin gave up everything for love, even his own dreams. To win a better future, he sent his younger brother away to study, while their parents sacrificed everything to support that hope. A decade later, the brother returns as a billionaire, ready to repay the debt of love and loyalty. But just when Elvin is finally ready to marry the woman who waited for him all these years, a powerful rival named Christopher threatens to steal everything.
